OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSome
OL,6,Fshowers Friday night, clearing
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards early Saturday. Patchy
OL,8,Frain at times in the far northwest,
OL,9,Fand some coastal mist patches.
OL,10,FOtherwise dry. Hot sunshine by day,
OL,11,Fmostly clear overnight.
